meta.description: Calculate the maximum amount of electricity that can be transmitted from Station 0 (source) to Station 7 (destination) in a network of power stations, ensuring that the flow through each transmission line does not exceed its capacity.

sets.name: STATIONS
sets.description: Set of power stations in the network.

params.name: capacity
params.description: Capacity of transmission lines between stations in megawatts.

vars.name: flow
vars.description: Flow of electricity in megawatts between stations.

objective.name: max_total_flow
objective.description: Maximize the total flow of electricity from Station 0 to Station 7.
